text:
"The president of the United States and White House staff are...very often tested—or at least given the option to get tested—for the virus, and surrounded by the nation’s best scientists and physicians," writes @LawrenceGostin. 

"It wasn’t enough." https://t.co/t1EenkBaqJ

name: thedailybeast
text:
Joe Biden wanted to talk about the economy in Michigan. But he started with an announcement about his health.
“I got two COVID tests this morning,” he said. “One in Delaware and one by the former White House doc who came up, and everything’s cleared.” https://t.co/z0WpgHP1AT
